title: Kane Brown on Getting JACKED Working Out and Finding Songwriter in Instagram DMs + Red Flag Favorite TV Shows + Raymundo Got Offered $200 to Promote a Product on Instagram BUT there’s a problem…
itunes:title: Kane Brown on Getting JACKED Working Out and Finding Songwriter in Instagram DMs + Red Flag Favorite TV Shows + Raymundo Got Offered $200 to Promote a Product on Instagram BUT there’s a problem…
description:
Kane Brown stops by as the Friday Morning Conversation to talk about his new song “One Mississippi”, starting a publishing company and what motivated him to get ripped out. We answer the question: You're on a first date with someone and they tell you the name of their favorite TV show. You immediately leave. What's the Show? Raymundo tells us about a product he got offered to post about on Instagram but the issue he is having with it.
